description: We are streaming live worldwide over the internet and the chat room is packed. Some people are taking the day off from work to tune in. It’s the middle of the night on the other side of the world and some folks are staying up for the show. Brenn Wyson is an unpredictable dom who has a mind of his own. This is Vince Ferelli’s last porn shoot before he moves into independent horror flicks. And, Chad Rock is a gold mine when it comes to corporal punishment. He says to Brenn during the live show, “You can’t hurt me with that, Sir.” and all hell breaks loose. Members in the chat room are calling the shots, and it’s one hot shoot.
title: You can't hurt me with that, Sir. Live Shoot
